Package: wickragenome
Type: Package
Title: A Vector Database of the Market over the Streaming Indicators
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-genome over its C ABI hub: every asset a live
    vector over the streaming indicators, with similarity search, clustering and
    anomaly detection - byte-identical to the CLI and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-genome
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-genome/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-genome C ABI shared library (WKGENOME_LIB)
    and its header (WKGENOME_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
